      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ قَوْلِ اللَّهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ وَ هَدَيْناهُ النَّجْدَيْنِ قَالَ نَجْدَ الْخَيْرِ وَ الشَّرِّ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from Yunus Bin Abdul Rahman, from Ibn Bukeyr, from Hamza Bin Muhammad, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup>, said, ‘I asked him<sup>asws</sup> about the Words of Allah<sup>azwj</sup> Mighty and Majestic <span class=\"ibTxt\"><a href=\"/#/books/quran:90#h10\"><a href=\"/books/quran:90#h10\">[90:10]</a></a> And pointed out to him the two conspicuous ways</span>, he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The way of good and the evil’."
        ]
      }
    },
